<p><a name="History" id="History"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Caliphate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: History">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">History</span></h2>
<table class="toccolours" id="WSerie_Islam" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="0" width="170px" style="float: right; margin: 0 0 1em 1em; text-align:left; border: 1px solid #060; clear: right;">
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="font-size: 95%">
<p><small>Part of a <a href="/wiki/Category:Fiqh" title="Category:Fiqh">series</a> on the</small> <span style="font-size: 130%"><br />
<b><a href="/wiki/Fiqh" title="Fiqh">Islamic Jurisprudence</a></b></span><br />
– a <a href="/wiki/Academic_discipline" title="Academic discipline" class="mw-redirect">discipline</a> of <a href="/wiki/Islamic_studies" title="Islamic studies">Islamic studies</a></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="font-size: 95%; background-color:rgb(220, 245, 220); border-top:1px dashed #686"><b>Fields</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="font-size: 90%;">
<ul>
<li><b><a href="/wiki/Islamic_economic_jurisprudence" title="Islamic economic jurisprudence">Economic</a></b></li>
<li><b><a href="/wiki/Islamic_political_jurisprudence" title="Islamic political jurisprudence" class="mw-redirect">Political</a></b>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Political_aspects_of_Islam" title="Political aspects of Islam">Political Aspects</a></li>
<li><strong class="selflink">Caliphate</strong></li>
